methods.name: public Builder setMaxSuggestionCount(int value)
methods.comment:
* Max number of suggestions expected from the response. It must be a positive value. * Defaults to {@code SUGGESTION_COUNT_UNLIMITED} if not set. * *

In practice, it is recommended that the max suggestion count does not exceed 5 * for performance reasons.

methods.name: public Builder setInlinePresentationSpecs(@NonNull List<InlinePresentationSpec> value)
methods.comment:
* The {@link InlinePresentationSpec} for each suggestion in the response. If the max suggestion
         * count is larger than the number of specs in the list, then the last spec is used for the
         * remainder of the suggestions. The list should not be empty.

methods.name: Builder setHostPackageName(@NonNull String value)
methods.comment:
* The package name of the app that requests for the inline suggestions and will host the
         * embedded suggestion views. The app does not have to set the value for the field because
         * it'll be set by the system for safety reasons.

methods.name: public Builder setSupportedLocales(@NonNull LocaleList value)
methods.comment:
* The IME provided locales for the request. If non-empty, the inline suggestions should * return languages from the supported locales. If not provided, it'll default to be empty if * target SDK is S or above, and default to system locale otherwise. * *

Note for Autofill Providers: It is recommended for the returned inline suggestions * to have one locale to guarantee consistent UI rendering.

methods.name: public Builder setExtras(@NonNull Bundle value)
methods.comment:
* The extras state propagated from the IME to pass extra data. * *

Note: There should be no remote objects in the bundle, all included remote objects will * be removed from the bundle before transmission.

methods.name: Builder setHostInputToken(@NonNull IBinder value)
methods.comment:
* The host input token of the IME that made the request. This will be set by the system for
         * safety reasons.
         *
         * @hide

methods.name: Builder setHostDisplayId(int value)
methods.comment:
* The host display id of the IME that made the request. This will be set by the system for
         * safety reasons.
         *
         * @hide

methods.name: public Builder setInlineTooltipPresentationSpec(@NonNull InlinePresentationSpec value)
methods.comment: * Specifies the UI specification for the inline suggestion tooltip in the response.

methods.name: public InlineSuggestionsRequest build()
methods.comment: Builds the instance. This builder should not be touched after calling this!
